com.avaya.jtapi.tsapi.adapters

Class CallCenterCallListenerAdapter

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.avaya.jtapi.tsapi.adapters.CallListenerAdapter
      • com.avaya.jtapi.tsapi.adapters.CallCenterCallListenerAdapter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.util.EventListener, CallCenterCallListener, CallListener

    public class CallCenterCallListenerAdapter
extends CallListenerAdapter
implements CallCenterCallListener
    An adapter which is notified of all changes to the CallCenterCall object. The methods in this class are empty; this class is provided as a convenience for easily creating listeners by extending this class and overriding only the methods of interest.
    See Also:
    CallCenterCallListener
